<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>工单回复通知 | Apocalypse Flyleague</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0; padding:0; font-family:'SF Pro Display', 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; background-color:#f4f7f6; color:#1d1d1f;">

  <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
    <tr><td align="center" style="padding:40px 0;">

      <table width="700" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color:#ffffff; border-radius:20px; box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); overflow:hidden;">
        <tr>
          <td align="center" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#06C755,#3fc07b); color:#ffffff; padding:30px 0; font-size:26px; font-weight:700;">
            Apocalypse Flyleague<br>
            <span style="font-size:16px; opacity:0.9;">技术支持 · 工单回复</span>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- Content -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:40px 60px; font-size:16px; line-height:1.75;">
            <p>尊敬的 <strong>{{.Cid}}</strong>: </p>
            <p>您好，</p>
            <br>
            <p>您的工单"{{.Title}}"已被回复</p>
            <div style="margin:30px 0; padding:20px; border-radius:12px; background-color:#f0fdf4; border:1px solid #b7ebc4;">
              <p style="margin:0; font-weight:600; color:#057c3b;">回复内容如下:</p>
              <p style="margin-top:8px;">{{.Reply}}</p>
            </div>
            <br>
            <p>以上，<br>
            Apocalypse Flyleague · 技术支持</p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <tr>
          <td align="center" style="background-color:#f9fafb; padding:20px; font-size:13px; color:#86868b;">
            此邮件由系统自动发送，请勿直接回复<br>
            © 2025 Apocalypse Flyleague. All rights reserved.
          </td>
        </tr>

      </table>

    </td></tr>
  </table>

</body>
</html>
